with aluminium,</li><li id="li3" translate="yes">Do your best to avoid sanding down to the aluminium,</li><li id="li4" translate="yes">You <b translate="yes">MUST apply (within 1 hour and 30 minutes)</b> an "I-ALPHA and I-ALPHA reactive thinner" type pre-treatment primer and a "2K" type primer <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3542379"><linkdesc>vehicle: parts and consumables for the repair</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-002445</linkvalue></sieref> <b translate="yes">in the case of stripped aluminium</b>.</li></ul></noteR><noteR translate="no" type="warning"><para id="par2" translate="yes">Stripped aluminium (after straightening and/or sanding) is quickly covered with a transparent alumina film that gradually transforms into white aluminium oxide known as aluminium hydroxide.</para><para id="par3" translate="yes">This alumina film significantly alters the adhesion of paint products, adhesives or sealants.</para><para id="par4" translate="yes">Chemical paint stripping of stripped areas using an "I-ALPHA and I-ALPHA reactive thinner" type pre-treatment <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3542379" translate="no"><linkdesc translate="no">vehicle: parts and consumables for the repair</linkdesc><linkvalue translate="no">GIEMR-002445</linkvalue></sieref> is <b translate="yes">ESSENTIAL</b> to remove the aluminium hydroxide and <b translate="yes">ensure the adhesion of the paint</b>.</para></noteR><descsection translate="no"><para translate="yes"><b translate="yes">Areas particularly sensitive to corrosion:</b></para><ul translate="no"><li translate="yes">Areas within <technicalvalue translate="no"><value translate="yes">20</value><uom translate="yes">mm</uom></technicalvalue> of cuts, crimps, and edges of parts need to be treated with particular care. Make the maximum effort not to sand down to the aluminium.</li></ul><figure id="fig1" translate="no"><image dimension="F3 (180x120) #" href="../MergedPictures/ILL-000367132.PNG" style="width: 180.0mm; height: 120.0mm;" translate="no"/><illusnum>RDE-000315852-01-000367132</illusnum><?Pub Caret -1?></figure></descsection></descbody><description id="d1e41" translate="no"><title translate="yes">in case of scratches</title><descbody translate="no"><table colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1" translate="no"><tgroup cols="3" colsep="1" rowsep="1" translate="no"><colspec colname="1" colnum="1" colwidth="11.104839847608298%" translate="no"/><colspec colname="2" colnum="2" colwidth="44.447580076195855%" translate="no"/><colspec colname="3" colnum="3" colwidth="44.447580076195855%" translate="no"/><thead translate="no"><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes"><para translate="yes">Step</para></entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes"><para translate="yes">Description</para></entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes"><para translate="yes">Special notes</para></entry></row></thead><tbody translate="no"><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">1</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Smooth over the scratch</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">According to the technical sheet recommendations - Aluminium oxide based paper</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">2</para>               </entry><entry nameend="3" namest="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Wipe / blow</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">3</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Degrease</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Lint-free cloth soaked in surface cleaner <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3542379"><linkdesc>vehicle: parts and consumables for the repair</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-002445</linkvalue></sieref> (04B, Consumables - Products). Wipe with a dry lint-free cloth</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">4</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Apply and sand polyester mastic if necessary</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes"> <para translate="yes"> <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3464478"><linkdesc>bodywork finishing product : description</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-001818</linkvalue></sieref>(40A, General information) <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3542379"><linkdesc>vehicle: parts and consumables for the repair</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-002445</linkvalue></sieref> (04B, Consumables - Products)</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">5</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Masking</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Masking paper</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">6</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Apply a pre-treatment primer if the panel is bare</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes"> <para translate="yes"> <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3542379"><linkdesc>vehicle: parts and consumables for the repair</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-002445</linkvalue></sieref>(04B, Consumables - Products)</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">7</para>               </entry><entry nameend="3" namest="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Remove solvent</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">8</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Apply a bi-component primer</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes"> <para translate="yes"> <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3542379"><linkdesc>vehicle: parts and consumables for the repair</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-002445</linkvalue></sieref>(04B, Consumables - Products)</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">9</para>               </entry><entry nameend="3" namest="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Remove solvent / Dry</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">10</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Sand the primer</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">According to the technical sheet recommendations - Aluminium oxide based paper</para>          </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">11</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Sand the whole component</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">According to the technical sheet recommendations - Aluminium oxide based paper</para></entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">12</para>               </entry><entry nameend="3" namest="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Wipe / blow</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">13</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Degrease</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Lint-free cloth soaked in surface cleaner <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3542379"><linkdesc>vehicle: parts and consumables for the repair</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-002445</linkvalue></sieref> (04B, Consumables - Products). Wipe with a dry lint-free cloth</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">14</para>               </entry><entry colname="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Masking</para>               </entry><entry colname="3" translate="yes"> <para translate="yes"> <sieref href="x-wc://gie=OR:wt.part.WTPartMaster:3536705"><linkdesc>masking : description</linkdesc><linkvalue>GIEMR-001518</linkvalue></sieref> </para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="1" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">15</para>               </entry><entry nameend="3" namest="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Blow / rub with an abrasive pad</para>               </entry></row><row rowsep="0" translate="no"><entry colname="1" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">16</para>               </entry><entry nameend="3" namest="2" translate="yes">                 <para translate="yes">Apply the finishing paint</para>               </entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></descbody></description><descriptio